This module serves the common part driver of spm

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
This module creates one executable binary files for loading/initializing the firmwares including
spm if needed.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:


HOW TO USE IT?
==============
the executable binary files, spm_loader, will be started in init.rc when boot. it will load/initialize
to load the firmwares of spm

The source code was written by MediaTek.
